<materialsCitation pageId="2" pageNumber="227">Andunde (Bundundi) Semliki River, west of Ruwenzori, Congo Belge (about 0°40’N 29°40’E, near the Semliki River, North-Kivu Province, DR Congo).</materialsCitation>
