<subSubSection lastPageId="3" lastPageNumber="228" pageId="2" pageNumber="227" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="2.[1388,2593,3090,3241]" pageId="2" pageNumber="227">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1388,1643,3129,3162]" pageId="2" pageNumber="227">Descriptive notes.</emphasis>
Head-body 242-303 mm, tail 220-265 mm, ear 29-34 mm, hindfoot 81-91 mm. No specific data are available for body weight. Tail of the Whitetailed Sengi is ¢.90% of head-body length and is proximally thick and distally
</paragraph>
